{"tid":2486001,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經新聞：理智基金「連燈力」於開市後以$254.67果斷精準撈底買入MSFT！聽取有心軍師意見必有所得！","createTime":"2021-04-12T14:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T14:15:08.000Z","uid":149018,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0092333b0d562a4ec887cc2162b3e5d3f3407e","tid":2486001,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T14:29:27.000Z","msg":"第三十一次軍議<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcAnR424CxSDCc3zwbdqMSP85sNU1sdMLmuc4tcbGFgpc?filename=FKDeH2v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKDeH2v.jpg&h=43f2a775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmamNmNPy7suN18eNBxVziwBZaSvNRG3HipopXnSXsviMW?filename=qbTKkO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqbTKkO8.jpg&h=f8610dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呂布第三十戰與YINN大戰三百回合未能分出勝負，再戰亦無益處故小損1.58%離場YINN，未有傷及軍隊命脈。<br />\n第三十一次軍議，有眾軍師如「我唔撚玩啦」「價值投資客」進柬BABA，認為&quot;阿里巴巴與維尼外交商議大成功，BABA進貢維尼後港股BABA表演勇猛&quot; 奉先表示認同但未及於盤前暴升前入市故認為獲利不多，若為昨已持有定必入陣。<br />\n此後呂布於MSFT及TQQQ中考慮及找尋入陣最佳時機，終於22:05以$254.67精準撈底MSFT再顯其機智冷靜，此仗將冷靜行軍務求於明日盤前獲利。<br />\n<br />\n呂布軍「連燈力」目前戰況30戰12勝18敗，勝率現為<span class=\"red\">40.00</span>%！<br />\n目前「連燈力」呂布狀態：<br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"red\">683.41</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">-31.66</span>%<br />\n<br />\n呂布小敗機智退兵，智力微減，武力100 智力<span class=\"red\">67</span>操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"green\">呂布曰：董卓?曹操?可笑，出師未捷身先死，奉先從未畏懼。</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmchfnLpcVKAPD6EBfB5Bwt9d81Q3n4tE7s8yFFBGrCVHk?filename=zOVD9L4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzOVD9L4.jpg&h=ef0b087f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac8f310c32f3c8ca900c8283ca7f9ffe4fc11f7c","tid":2486001,"uid":8662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-12T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"主公好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21685bf